                <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">pr</supplied>o salute <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> <expan><abbr>Calp</abbr><ex>urni</ex></expan> H<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied>no<lb break="no" n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">r</supplied><expan><abbr>atiani</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecti</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VII <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audiae</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Ingenu<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>rarius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>egionis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>fact</abbr><ex cert="low">us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ab</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> <expan><abbr>eo</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>et exacti co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarii</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>frum</abbr><ex>entarii</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>no <expan><abbr>et</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> <lb n="2"/>Rufo co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Vorderseite und rechte Nebenseite beschrieben. Z. 2/3: möglicherweise auch Hono(---) / Tatiani zu lesen; Z. 6 (Anfang): statt L auch B, statt G auch O möglich; Z. 7: Buchsteben teils schlecht erkennbar; Z. 8: von et sind nur zwei senkrechte Hasten erkennbar. Datierung: möglicherweise waren als Konsuln Mamertinus und Rufus (182 n. Chr.) angegeben.</p>
            </div>
